SUMMARY:Self Defense Class
DESCRIPTION:This is a safe\, inclusive opportunity to learn self defense from a dedicated group of martial arts practitioners at the Davis Arts Center. If you have ever felt like you would like to learn a little more about how to defend yourself and your loved ones\, and would like to get a little fitness training too\, please join us! No experience necessary\, start any time. We ask for a $10 donation per class\, but you can pay whatever you can. \n 
