SUMMARY:Astronomy on Tap Davis
DESCRIPTION:Our next Astronomy on Tap Davis\, CA will be Thursday April 2nd\, 6-8pm at Sudwerk\, and we have our two speakers: Professor Dan Cebra will talk about Galactic cosmic rays and how they impact space exploration\, and Sukanya Chakrabarti will speak about dark matter. As always we will also have astronomy in the news\, trivia\, and a raffle. Free and open to all ages\, come down to Sudwerk on April 2nd!
